# Module introduction

We will turn online only application into an offline application by adding a service worker. And we will learn how you configure it to fully meet your needs.

It's rendering a list of dummy block posts which are fetched in our app component with jsonplaceholder.

If we inspect our app in chrome we can go to the application tab and turn it to offline mode. This is in developer tools. This will simulate no internet connection.

We can use a service worker to to the app with angular.